      "span_text": "The correlation between the actual subsequent slope and that predicted by the model for each participant was compared against the equivalent correlation for MD predicting the subsequent slope of MD, to determine whether the index demonstrated significantly better predictability, using the Z Ã 2 test statistic  ."
